te the boss for a big paycheck.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gear Up and Roll Out</strong></h2>Gain experience from killing bugs and upgrade your abilities. Customize your Exterminator to fit your play style and kill even more bugs.<br><br>What are you waiting for? Wishlist the game NOW!",
